unexpectedly, the match is interrupted by a group of armed soldiers from 2051

00:00:32.978 --> 00:00:35.762
they appear on the soccer field in a burst of light and smoke

00:00:35.858 --> 00:00:38.450
and announce that 30 years into the future

00:00:38.546 --> 00:00:42.338
the planet Earth is invaded by an alien race called the "Whitespikes"

