these are voracious and brutal creatures 

00:00:44.594 --> 00:00:48.050
whose only motivation is to destroy all life around them

00:00:48.146 --> 00:00:53.090
to balance the scales, the future soldiers have traveled to ask the present planet for help

00:00:53.282 --> 00:00:56.210
in response, nations work together to save humanity

00:00:56.306 --> 00:01:01.010
building time travel facilities and recruiting soldiers to fight the future war

00:01:01.154 --> 00:01:05.954
unfortunately, many batches of military forces have been sent to the future for duty

00:01:06.146 --> 00:01:10.658
but most of them lost their lives in the battle and only very few managed to come back

00:01:10.802 --> 00:01:13.010
eventually, a world draft begins 

00:01:13.058 --> 00:01:16.898
and groups of ordinary men and veterans are called forth for the mission 

00:01:17.234 --> 00:01:21.602
among those reluctantly recruited is Dan, a veteran of the Iraq War 

00:01:21.746 --> 00:01:23.714
Dan reports to the military base

00:01:23.858 --> 00:01:27.698
