that only those who have already died before the war starts are enlisted 

00:01:36.482 --> 00:01:39.410
and he will die in an accident in 2028 

00:01:39.554 --> 00:01:42.962
Dan returns home to bid farewell to his beloved daughter and wife 

00:01:43.058 --> 00:01:44.786
before leaving for the mission

00:01:45.034 --> 00:01:49.114
shortly after, Dan is thrown in with a group of fellow recruits for basic training

00:01:49.402 --> 00:01:52.378
as most of the recruits are civilians who can't use guns

