on their way out, the Whitespikes chase after them and devour a few soldiers

00:03:39.364 --> 00:03:43.492
to ensure the unit's safety, Dan decides to cover them by going last 

00:03:43.588 --> 00:03:47.620
a few seconds later, Dan is attacked by a rampaging Whitespike 

