after firing all of his bullets

00:03:49.444 --> 00:03:53.236
Dan takes out an ax from the fire hydrant cabinet for melee combat

00:03:53.332 --> 00:03:55.828
although the feeble and weak Dan spares no effort

00:03:55.924 --> 00:03:59.476
the vicious tentacled Whitespike keeps gaining the upper hand 

00:03:59.572 --> 00:04:04.372
when he is on the brink of losing his life, Charlie and Dorian come back to rescue him

00:04:04.612 --> 00:04:07.684
Charlie fires a volley of shots at the monster 

00:04:07.828 --> 00:04:11.572
as some bullets hit its belly and neck, the Achille's heel of Whitespikes

00:04:11.668 --> 00:04:14.164
the alien species falls to the ground 

