when the safe zone is within reach

00:04:49.828 --> 00:04:53.236
some wounded soldiers sacrifice themselves to tackle the beasts 

00:04:53.284 --> 00:04:56.116
so that rest can safely leave with the toxin

00:04:56.260 --> 00:04:58.516
just when Dan steps into the safe zone

00:04:58.612 --> 00:05:02.452
the deafening explosion takes place, knocking him unconscious

00:05:02.596 --> 00:05:06.436
he then wakes up in sickbay, with Charlie and Dorian beside him 

00:05:06.532 --> 00:05:10.420
in this military encampment, Dan extends his appreciation to Colonel 

