firing machine guns at the hordes of monsters on top of the vehicle

00:06:51.127 --> 00:06:56.839
their destination is a military base built on the sea, the last military base left on Earth 

00:06:57.031 --> 00:07:01.255
with concerted effort, Colonel and her colleagues come up with a scientific solution 

00:07:01.351 --> 00:07:03.511
that can kill the female Whitespike 

00:07:03.655 --> 00:07:07.495
however, the smidgen of hope of actually wiping out the enemy shatters 

