when time is so pressing,  Colonel is injured by a spikey bullet 

00:07:27.031 --> 00:07:29.863
with only five minutes left before his departure

00:07:29.959 --> 00:07:33.127
Dan quickly brings Colonel up and prepares to go 

00:07:33.223 --> 00:07:37.735
all of a sudden, the once caged female Whitespike appears before them to seize Colonel 

