in other words, human beings in 30 years' future are defeated and doomed

00:08:17.431 --> 00:08:20.551
knowing this, Dan returns home with a heavy heart 

00:08:20.743 --> 00:08:25.879
his wife burst into tears of joy to have him back, but Dan is upset thinking of his daughter

00:08:25.975 --> 00:08:29.719
that night, Dan shares with his wife what he has gone through during the week of duty 

00:08:29.815 --> 00:08:32.119
and his resolution to save their daughter 

00:08:32.263 --> 00:08:33.463
as far as Dan knows

